snippet.textDisplay: "Sammi Meri Waar", felt like one of the most timeless love songs I have had the joy of experiencing on Coke Studio.  As an English speaking person(i.e., an American), having CC available for this song was especially great, and so appreciated. Lastly, in today's climate, a song -such as this - which promotes commitment and the willingness to offer one's life up for a loved one or your friends is simply mesmerizing in its context. (John 15:13) Much love!
